{"data":[{"id":560811545,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2620ef3880fd5c36157285d3bee14777","url_token":"nancy-16-40-68","name":"哼哧哼哧的辭","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b4cf50a32a31b5bb96b38571f0eef7d8_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b4cf50a32a31b5bb96b38571f0eef7d8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2620ef3880fd5c36157285d3bee14777","user_type":"people","headline":"开始你伟大的历险๑乛◡乛๑","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":5,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560811545","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545890056,"updated_time":1546009307,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":15,"comment_count":8,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"很多人在鼓励他，不要因为这次证明的结果，网友们的冷嘲热讽而改变自己对数学的初心。\u003cbr\u003e        但我看到的是一位希望借数学帮自己获取一些利益的高中生，他的初心真的是热爱纯粹的数学吗？抱歉我觉得不是。\u003cbr\u003e        他让我看到的，一方面是取巧心理在作祟。\u003cbr\u003e明明想要考上清华北大可以靠自己的努力，走很多人常规的途径，从高考考进去，但是从他个人主页显示的信息看来，他并不踏实于此。私以为，他只是一个在高中生身份中成绩平平却又想“抄近路”的人而已。\u003cbr\u003e        如果想要走和大多数人不一样的路来达到自己的目标也无可厚非，问出这样的问题只是信息缺少，想要找到招生办的老师也完全可以。但是更合理的方式应该是，提问前先让周围可能可以提供帮助的老师帮忙验证过程。而不是在知乎掀起哗然大波，再用“你们都是错的，你们等着被我打脸”的态度，和大家约定时间发布证明，一个发布前并没有给其他人验证过的证明，一个让大家抱着“看好戏”或是支持鼓励心态来等待的时间。\u003cbr\u003e问出这样的问题，眼界还是太浅。\u003cbr\u003e另一方面，则是对数学缺少敬畏。所以他的态度很容易让人觉得不舒服。哥德巴赫猜想不应该和“保送清华北大”摆在同一个地位上相提并论。（当然，我并不是说这两所大学不够顶尖。只是孰轻孰重大家都知道。）\u003cbr\u003e只是，哥德巴赫猜想应该是纯粹的，不应该被拿来和钓名沽誉的事情联系在一起的存在。\u003cbr\u003e一旦存在目的，就不对劲了。\u003cbr\u003e以上。","editable_content":"","excerpt":"很多人在鼓励他，不要因为这次证明的结果，网友们的冷嘲热讽而改变自己对数学的初心。 但我看到的是一位希望借数学帮自己获取一些利益的高中生，他的初心真的是热爱纯粹的数学吗？抱歉我觉得不是。 他让我看到的，一方面是取巧心理在作祟。 明明想要考上清…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=113\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url